# shadcn/ui Rules

## Core Principles
- Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui`
- Follow shadcn component patterns and API
- Extend components when needed, maintain compatibility
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling (no inline styles)

## Component Import

### Standard Import Pattern
```javascript
// Single component
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';

// Multiple components
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '@/components/ui/card';

// Form components
import {
  Form,
  FormControl,
  FormField,
  FormItem,
  FormLabel,
  FormMessage
} from '@/components/ui/form';
```

## Component Usage

### Button
```javascript
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';

<Button variant="default" size="default">
  Click me
</Button>

// Variants: default, destructive, outline, secondary, ghost, link
// Sizes: default, sm, lg, icon, icon-sm, icon-lg
```

### Card
```javascript
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '@/components/ui/card';

<Card>
  <CardHeader>
    <CardTitle>Title</CardTitle>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    Content
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```

### Form Components
```javascript
import {
  Form,
  FormField,
  FormItem,
  FormLabel,
  FormControl,
  FormMessage
} from '@/components/ui/form';

<Form {...form}>
  <FormField
    control={form.control}
    name="fieldName"
    render={({ field }) => (
      <FormItem>
        <FormLabel>Label</FormLabel>
        <FormControl>
          <Input {...field} />
        </FormControl>
        <FormMessage />
      </FormItem>
    )}
  />
</Form>
```

## Styling

### Tailwind CSS Only
- Use Tailwind utility classes
- Use `cn()` utility for className merging
- Use theme variables: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`
- Support dark mode: `dark:bg-background`

### Common Patterns
```javascript
// Container
className="bg-background min-h-screen p-4"

// Card
className="rounded-lg border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm"

// Text
className="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight"
className="text-muted-foreground text-sm"

// Spacing
className="space-y-4" // Vertical
className="gap-4" // Flex/Grid
```

## Component Extension

### Modifying Components
- Edit components in `src/components/ui/[component].jsx`
- Maintain shadcn API compatibility
- Use `cn()` for className merging
- Follow shadcn component structure

### Example Extension
```javascript
// src/components/ui/button.jsx
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils';
import { buttonVariants } from './button';

function Button({ className, variant, size, ...props }) {
  return (
    <button
      className={cn(buttonVariants({ variant, size }), className)}
      {...props}
    />
  );
}
```

