## Icons

### Icon Library
- Use `lucide-react` for icons (configured in components.json)
- Import from `lucide-react`

```javascript
import { Mail, Lock, Eye, EyeOff } from 'lucide-react';

<Mail className="h-4 w-4" />
```

### Icon Sizing
- Use Tailwind size classes: `h-4 w-4`, `h-5 w-5`
- Or use `size-4`, `size-5` (if available)

## Best Practices

### DO
- Use shadcn components as building blocks
- Follow shadcn component patterns
- Use Tailwind for all styling
- Support dark mode
- Use theme variables

### DON'T
- Don't use inline styles
- Don't modify shadcn components unnecessarily
- Don't break component API
- Don't mix styling approaches

## Adding New Components

### Using shadcn CLI
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]
```

### Manual Addition
- Copy component from shadcn docs
- Place in `src/components/ui/[component].jsx`
- Follow existing component patterns
- Update exports if needed

## Component Configuration

### components.json
```json
